built from the ground up.

00:01:13.660 --> 00:01:16.780 align:middle line:84%
Training programs started
when I was like, four

00:01:16.780 --> 00:01:18.310 align:middle line:90%
or five years old.

00:01:18.310 --> 00:01:20.890 align:middle line:84%
Training program went
until I was 17 years old.

00:01:20.890 --> 00:01:23.320 align:middle line:84%
And at 17 years old I
was deployed actually

00:01:23.320 --> 00:01:26.530 align:middle line:84%
into the covert military
space program, sent to Mars

00:01:26.530 --> 00:01:28.630 align:middle line:90%
for 17 years to be in the MDF.

00:01:28.630 --> 00:01:30.840 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Wait a
minute, wait a minute.

00:01:30.840 --> 00:01:32.030 align:middle line:90%
Sent to Mars?

00:01:32.030 --> 00:01:33.010 align:middle line:90%
>>CRAMER: Yes.

00:01:33.010 --> 00:01:34.850 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: How were
you sent to Mars?

00:01:34.850 --> 00:01:36.100 align:middle line:90%
>>CRAMER: Oh, well, via a--

00:01:36.100 --> 00:01:37.180 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: In a space ship?

00:01:37.180 --> 00:01:40.000 align:middle line:84%
>>CRAMER: Via a transport
ship from the Moon,

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:43.640 align:middle line:84%
