personnel on it at that time.

00:01:48.194 --> 00:01:49.860 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What year
might that have been?

00:01:49.860 --> 00:01:51.550 align:middle line:84%
>>CRAMER: That would
have been in 1987.

00:01:51.550 --> 00:01:52.870 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: All right, continue.

00:01:52.870 --> 00:01:55.490 align:middle line:84%
>>CRAMER: So we were put
onto a transport ship.

00:01:55.490 --> 00:02:00.310 align:middle line:84%
Again, I'm guessing about 4,000
or 5,000 people it held total.

00:02:00.310 --> 00:02:02.830 align:middle line:84%
And then that ship took off
from Lunar Operations Command

00:02:02.830 --> 00:02:03.730 align:middle line:90%
on the Moon.

00:02:03.730 --> 00:02:06.880 align:middle line:84%
