would get a letter from the FBI

00:04:21.480 --> 00:04:23.890 align:middle line:84%
or from the CMCs office
telling me to cease and desist.

00:04:23.890 --> 00:04:25.260 align:middle line:84%
And then my attorney
and I, we could get

00:04:25.260 --> 00:04:26.468 align:middle line:90%
into that whole conversation.

00:04:26.468 --> 00:04:28.860 align:middle line:84%
But no one sent me any
letters because I'm not

00:04:28.860 --> 00:04:29.910 align:middle line:90%
committing fraud.

00:04:29.910 --> 00:04:32.368 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: So you're not making
a million dollars doing this.

00:04:32.368 --> 00:04:33.180 align:middle line:90%
>>CRAMER: No.

00:04:33.180 --> 00:04:35.370 align:middle line:90%
Are you kidding me?

00:04:35.370 --> 00:04:37.920 align:middle line:84%
I do a few speaking events
and a few interviews.

00:04:37.920 --> 00:04:39.480 align:middle line:84%
And no, I don't
get paid anything.

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:41.910 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What do you do
in your normal "life"

00:04:41.910 --> 00:04:43.592 align:middle line:90%
in terms of job or career?

00:04:43.592 --> 00:04:46.050 align:middle line:84%
>>CRAMER: Oh, I have to work
a day job at the moment, which

00:04:46.050 --> 00:04:46.980 align:middle line:90%
isn't any fun.

00:04:46.980 --> 00:04:49.230 align:middle line:84%
But you know, it's what I
have to do to pay the bills.

00:04:49.230 --> 00:04:51.300 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Does that
day job conflict

00:04:51.300 --> 00:04:56.250 align:middle line:84%
with this story in the point
where people that you work with

00:04:56.250 --> 00:04:59.160 align:middle line:90%
go, Randy, what is this?

00:04:59.160 --> 00:05:01.590 align:middle line:84%
>>CRAMER: Oh, I don't talk to
people at my day job about--

00:05:01.590 --> 00:05:03.090 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What if
they see this show?

00:05:03.090 --> 00:05:05.423 align:middle line:84%
>>CRAMER: Well, then we'll
have a conversation about it.

00:05:05.423 --> 00:05:07.260 align:middle line:84%
I'm perfectly open to
always talk about it

00:05:07.260 --> 00:05:08.926 align:middle line:84%
with anybody who wants
to talk about it.

00:05:08.926 --> 00:05:10.320 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I don't
shy away from it.

00:05:10.320 --> 00:05:14.580 align:middle line:84%
But I don't want to create
attention in a situation

00:05:14.580 --> 00:05:15.840 align:middle line:90%
where I don't need attention.

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:17.884 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I'm not an
attention grabber

00:05:17.884 --> 00:05:20.050 align:middle line:84%
so I don't go around telling
people, I went to Mars.

00:05:20.050 --> 00:05:22.140 align:middle line:84%
I mean, it's just not
that big of a deal to me.

00:05:22.140 --> 00:05:23.340 align:middle line:84%
But when people want
to talk about it,

00:05:23.340 --> 00:05:24.380 align:middle line:90%
I'm more than happy to talk.

00:05:24.380 --> 00:05:26.588 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: So you're really
you're not gaining anything

00:05:26.588 --> 00:05:27.990 align:middle line:90%
